Statistics-Suggest version 0.01
===============================

INSTALLATION

Download SUGGEST from http://glaros.dtc.umn.edu/gkhome/suggest/download

Find libsuggest.a which matches your environment and place it under
your library path (or specify its path with LIBS option as shown below).

Then do:

   perl Makefile.PL [LIBS='-L/where/to/find/libsuggest.a -lsuggest']
   make
   make test
   make install


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  libsuggest.a from SUGGEST

